# Licence

This repository is intended to be released as an open educational and research project.

Until a final licence is formally confirmed, use the following provisional licensing intention:

## Educational and research content

All written educational, research and curriculum content is intended to be released under:

**Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (CC BY 4.0)**

This allows others to share and adapt the material, including commercially, provided appropriate credit is given.

## Software, scripts and technical tooling

Any code, scripts or technical tooling added to this repository are intended to be released under:

**MIT Licence**

## Before public launch

Before the first public release, replace this provisional notice with final licence text and confirm that all contributors understand the licensing model.

## Attribution

Recommended attribution format:

> Adapted from Year Zero Education, Version [x], [repository URL], licensed under [final licence].
